column207: The issue with this method is the use of the continue statement in the do while. When it checks if the letter in the current slot is the same as the specified character, if it finds that the character equals the current letter, it will start the loop over with the continue statement, jumping back to the top of the "do". Yet the critical error here is that the iterator does not iterate when doing this continue, so it will start the loop over, only to continue again since the iterator and letter have not changed. It becomes stuck in an infinite loop of continues.
